CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 11, 1958, pg. A23, reads: "PITT AKAS - These young ladies are members of the Iota Chapter of the Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority at the University of Pittsburgh. Taking time out after discussing plans for their 'Harvest Hop' at North Park Lodge, Oct. 10, are, left to right, seated: Mae Louise Allen, Louella Blow, Lee West and Andrea Jones.  Standing: Shirley Mike, Frances Ruffin, Rosalia [Rosalie] Travis, Sarah Plowden and Lois Jeanne Dougan. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Kappa Alpha members, seated from left: Mae Louise Allen, Louella Blow, Lee Bertha West, and Andrea Loveda Jones; standing: Shirley Mike, Frances Ruffin, Rosalie Travis, Sarah Plowden, and Lois Jeanne Dougan (Tretiak), gathered on lawn at University of Pittsburgh with Fifth Avenue and the Pittsburgh Athletic Association building in background, another version
